# CyberVault DApp

CyberVault is a secure log-storage decentralized application built on Ethereum.

## Features
- Upload secure messages to blockchain
- Retrieve stored logs
- Neon cyber UI (Orbitron font)
- Ethers.js v5.7
- MetaMask wallet connection

## Contract Address
0xDdABb651130A26d318c33e4938d65f5cAc31d055

## How to Use
1. Open index.html in browser
2. Connect MetaMask
3. Enter a message
4. Click Upload or Retrieve Logs

#code

